*************************************
version-1.6.0

NEW FEATURES

   - Refactoring as python package #42
   - The --export parameter now takes a path with the output vcf file #34

BIG FIXES

   - Fix division by zero when effective genome size is 0 #35
   - Fix sys.stderr.write() incorrect signature in pyEffGenomeSize.py #36
   - Fix misleading exception handling that says skip but crashes #39
   - Fix getTag() using global variable instead of parameter #38
   - Fix bitwise AND instead of logical comparison #37

*************************************
version-1.5.0

NEW FEATURES

   - Add Strelka and VEP config file #20,#27

SIGNIFICANT USER CHANGES

   - Fix default values in `--vaf`, `--maf`, `--minDepth`, `--minAltDepth` #31
   - vaf, maf, minDepth and minAltDepth are now strictly defined
   - Update help message #28
   - Compress output vcf files (--export / --debug)

BUG FIXES

   - filterLowQual is not only based on the FILTER column. Only PASS variants are reported #21
   - fix bug with multi-allele freqs #25

